LifterLMS Icons
---------------

LifterLMS Icon library.

---

## CHANGELOG

[CHANGELOG](./CHANGELOG.md)


## Installation

```bash
npm install --save @lifterlms/icons`
```


## Usage

```jsx
import { Icon, lifterlms } from '@lifterlms/icons';

<Icon icon={ lifterlms } />;
```
